1.title: Introduction

episode of.title: Taoism: a Path to a Higher Dimension (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: In this course I offer to share with you some ancient powerful wisdom. A Chinese wisdom called Toaism or Daoism. This theory holds the key to reach higher levels of conciseness and tranquility. Just like most of my other courses, in this course I share with you some deep theory as well as its practical aspects.
